<F P=102>  BK2601113494 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam in English 1000 GMT 26 
Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK2601113494 </F>
<F P=104>  Hanoi Voice of Vietnam </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A retired Vietnamese general at the center of 
