Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Two more domestic airports Hanoi-Dien Bien in Lai 
Chau Province, and Hanoi-Na San in Son La Province will be 
reopened by mid-April. More than 1 billion dong (roughly 
$100,000) have been spent in rebuilding the Dien Bien Airport, 
and about $25,000 will be needed for the ugrading of the Na San 
Airport. 

