<F P=102>  BK2501115994 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network in Vietnamese 
0500 GMT 22 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK2501115994 </F>
<F P=104>  Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Vietnamese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Last year, our country's oil and gas sector 
exploited 6.3 million tons of crude oil, performed a 5,815-meter 
deep exploratory drill, completed the drilling of 17 oil wells, 
and started building a gas pipeline from the Bach Ho Oil Well to 
the hinterland. 
  This year, efforts will be made to exploit 6.7 million tons 
of crude oil, complete the drilling of 29 oil wells, and put 
four new oil rigs into operation. 

</TEXT>

