<F P=103> BK2501134794 </F>
<F P=104>  Bangkok Radio Thailand Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Thai </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Foreign Ministry has reported on Foreign 
Minister Squadron Leader Prasong Sunsiri's official visit to 
Brazil on 24 January as guest of the Brazilian foreign minister. 
According to the report, both sides agreed to expand bilateral 
relations, particularly in the fields of trade, investment, and 
tourism, and to broaden economic cooperation by setting up a 
commercial center in Sao Paolo. 
